data.description: Country living close to the city.This home has it all! 4 BR's,3 full-2 half Ba's. Beautiful arched ceiling in foyer,arched doorways through out downstairs. Formal DR,LR or Office.Large GR with wood burning fireplace (never used), large windows across back overlooking covered porch and in-ground gunite pool.Beautiful Sunroom.Large open floor plan,kitchen with granite counterops,beautiful cabinets,huge island & bar. Brazillian Cherry Hardwood floors, carpet in BR's only.Unique ceilings & specialized textured walls.Three BR's downstairs,upstairs is a bonus room,BR and BA. Wired workshp with roll up door and a lean-too. A large portion of the property is wooded for lots of privacy. This gorgeous home sits on 2.43 acres. Roof only 2 years old. Freshly painted. Double garage was enclosed to make a large man-cave,could be easily converted back to a garage. Tax card shows 3257 SF,but plans were altered & garage closed in to make it 4200sf. Spouse is licensed Realtor in the State of Ga.
